886
00:54:45,961 --> 00:54:47,905
- Five minutes, maybe ten.
- Yeah, if that.

887
00:54:48,005 --> 00:54:50,007
Okay, emergencies only.

888
00:54:51,008 --> 00:54:52,510
If something gets in the store.

889
00:55:00,267 --> 00:55:02,795
