921
00:57:13,984 --> 00:57:15,736
God!

922
00:57:16,612 --> 00:57:18,013
Oh, my God!
Oh, my God!

923
00:57:18,113 --> 00:57:20,115
David! David!

924
00:57:22,409 --> 00:57:23,435
<i>...you sure?</i>

925
00:57:23,535 --> 00:57:24,578
Look!

926
00:57:47,685 --> 00:57:49,144
My God.

927
00:58:04,201 --> 00:58:06,161
